PN,44101
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1781187095
OL,3,C'Significant numbers' of police to be
OL,4,Con streets of NI after disorder
OL,6,FPolice in Northern Ireland will be on
OL,7,Fthe streets in greater numbers after
OL,8,Ftwo days of disorder following a
OL,9,Fviolent knife attack in Belfast.
OL,11,FPolice from a number of forces from
OL,12,Facross the UK have arrived in Northern
OL,13,FIreland to support the PSNI with their
OL,14,Foperation to crack down on the
OL,15,Fviolence.
OL,17,FA senior officer also vowed officers
OL,18,Fwould catch all those responsible for
OL,19,Fthe violence which has seen people
OL,20,Fforced out of their homes, properties
OL,21,Fattacked and police injured.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1781187095
OL,3,C'Significant numbers' of police to be
OL,4,Con streets of NI after disorder
OL,6,FHe added: "The stakes for you are high
OL,7,F- we will bring you to justice."
OL,9,FTwelve police officers were injured
OL,10,Fand 16 arrests made following
OL,11,FWednesday night's unrest. That
OL,12,Fdisturbance was not on the same level
OL,13,Fwitnessed on Tuesday evening.
OL,15,FPSNI Assistant Chief Constable Ryan
OL,16,FHenderson told reporters the justice
OL,17,Fsystem "stands ready to give long
OL,18,Fsentences to those bringing disorder
OL,19,Fto our streets".
OL,26,@nD@KOUyD@HOU{D@OO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1781187095
OL,3,C'Significant numbers' of police to be
OL,4,Con streets of NI after disorder
OL,6,FHe added: "I want to strongly condemn
OL,7,Fthe second night of disorder, seen in
OL,8,Fsome areas across Northern Ireland.
OL,9,FThis violent behaviour by a thuggish
OL,10,Fminority will not be tolerated.
OL,12,FThere was "significant disorder" in
OL,13,FNewtownabbey and Portadown, he said.
OL,15,F"We, the police, used water cannon and
OL,16,Ffire 20 AEP to quell that disorder.
OL,18,F"It was clear from the outset that
OL,19,Fthose who attended were not intent on
OL,20,Fpeaceful protest, rather they were
OL,21,Fintent on violence."
OL,26,@nD@KOUwD@AOUzD@AOU}D@TO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1781187095
OL,3,C'Significant numbers' of police to be
OL,4,Con streets of NI after disorder
OL,6,FPolice have also released images of
OL,7,Ftwo people they'd like to speak to in
OL,8,Fconnection with "serious disorder" in
OL,9,FBelfast on Tuesday, June 9.
OL,11,FMore have also been charged to appear
OL,12,Fin court.
OL,14,FACC Henderson said more police would
OL,15,Fbe on the streets of Northern Ireland
OL,16,Fon Thursday evening.
OL,18,FHe added: "Tonight, we will be back on
OL,19,Fthe ground in significant numbers.
OL,26,@pD@QOUpD@bO]zD@KOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1781187095
OL,3,C'Significant numbers' of police to be
OL,4,Con streets of NI after disorder
OL,6,F"Our numbers, bolstered by our
OL,7,Fcolleagues from Great Britain, who are
OL,8,Fjoining us on mutual aid, will see
OL,9,Fofficers deployed all across Northern
OL,10,FIreland to protect our communities and
OL,11,Fto prevent disorder.
OL,13,F"Let me be clear, there can be
OL,14,Fpeaceful protest, it is part of a
OL,15,Fdemocratic society. What we saw bears
OL,16,Fno resemblance to that."
OL,18,FDuring the disorder, a nurse was
OL,19,Fchased and intimidated by masked thugs
OL,20,Fin a "racist attack" on her way to
OL,21,Fwork, a health trust has revealed.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUxD@XO]|D@FOU|D@TO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1781187095
OL,3,C'Significant numbers' of police to be
OL,4,Con streets of NI after disorder
OL,6,FThe South Eastern Trust said it was
OL,7,F"horrified" but commended the victim's
OL,8,Fcourage after the incident at the
OL,9,FUlster Hospital in Dundonald last
OL,10,Fnight.
OL,12,FIn a statement the Trust said: "This
OL,13,Fnurse bravely insisted on remaining in
OL,14,Fthe hospital to care for the most
OL,15,Fvulnerable in our community.
OL,17,F"Her behaviour is in stark contrast to
OL,18,Fthe behaviour of the people who
OL,19,Fterrified her as she tried to do her
OL,20,Fjob. The Trust values and champions
OL,21,Fdiversity and inclusion."
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@KO]tD@`OUyD@AOU}D@YO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1781187095
OL,3,C'Significant numbers' of police to be
OL,4,Con streets of NI after disorder
OL,6,FACC Henderson condemned the incident
OL,7,Fsaying the intimidation of healthcare
OL,8,Fworkers was "disgraceful". He said
OL,9,Fthey were the "backbone of our
OL,10,Fsociety".
OL,12,F"They are caring for our families, our
OL,13,Ffriends and our loved ones. We are
OL,14,Fhere to support them in the same way
OL,15,Fthey support us.
OL,17,F"Tonight, we will be increasing our
OL,18,Fpatrols of key areas. I have been
OL,19,Ftalking to colleagues within health
OL,20,Ftrusts and others to hear their
OL,21,Fconcerns about their staff welfare."
OL,26,@tD@AOUyD@AOU}D@dO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1781187095
OL,3,C'Significant numbers' of police to be
OL,4,Con streets of NI after disorder
OL,6,FHe added: "The streets of Northern
OL,7,FIreland need to return to calm and
OL,8,Forder. Our children need to feel safe
OL,9,Freturning to their schools. Businesses
OL,10,Fneed to feel they could open their
OL,11,Fdoors. Everyone with influence needs
OL,12,Fto do all in their power to get the
OL,13,Fthugs off our streets."
OL,15,FThe police chief also pointed to those
OL,16,F"stirring up young people" to engage
OL,17,Fin disorder, saying they needed to
OL,18,Fstop.
OL,26,@nD@KOUuD@WO]xD@AOUxD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1781187095
OL,3,C'Significant numbers' of police to be
OL,4,Con streets of NI after disorder
OL,6,FHe said social media companies also
OL,7,Fhad a role to play in stopping the
OL,8,Fspread of information. A list of
OL,9,Faddresses had been circulated online.
OL,10,FThe police officer said much of what
OL,11,Fwas circulating online was incorrect.
OL,13,FThose who are maybe stirring up young
OL,14,Fpeople, getting them out onto the
OL,15,Fstreets, bringing them out in masks to
OL,16,Ftry and hide their identity.
OL,18,F"You need to stop that behaviour,
OL,19,Fbecause you're going to put young
OL,20,Fpeople at risk of becoming part of the
OL,21,Fcriminal justice system."
OL,26,@zD@AOU}D@YO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/13
