OL,3,C'Significant numbers' of police to be
OL,4,Con streets of NI after disorder
OL,6,FSudanese refugee Hadi Alodid, 30, was
OL,7,Fin court on Wednesday, charged with
OL,8,Fthe attempted murder of Stephen
OL,9,FOgilvie.
OL,11,FBelfast Magistrates' Court heard Mr
OL,12,FOgilvie, 44, lost his left eye and
OL,13,Fsuffered damage to his right eye as
OL,14,Fwell as injuries to his face, neck and
OL,15,Fback.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
