PN,44111
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1781187095
OL,3,C'Significant numbers' of police to be
OL,4,Con streets of NI after disorder
OL,6,FProtests planned across Northern
OL,7,FIreland failed to materialise on
OL,8,FWednesday evening but there was major
OL,9,Fdisruption as businesses and schools
OL,10,Fshut early and transport services were
OL,11,Fsuspended.
OL,13,FOn Thursday in Stormont, home to
OL,14,FNorthern Ireland's power-sharing
OL,15,Fgovernment, Alliance MLA Sian
OL,16,FMulholland told the Communities
OL,17,FCommittee of how up to 500 people had
OL,18,Fpresented themselves to voluntary and
OL,19,Fchurch organisations as "homeless"
OL,20,Fafter their addresses were shared
OL,21,Fonline as "targets".
OL,26,@{D@YOU{D@bO]}D@KOU}D@SO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44112
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1781187095
OL,3,C'Significant numbers' of police to be
OL,4,Con streets of NI after disorder
OL,6,FA Housing Executive spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"Since the beginning of the recent
OL,8,Fcivil unrest, 29 households who
OL,9,Fpresented to us in need of housing
OL,10,Fsupport have been assisted.
OL,12,F"We are also aware others may have
OL,13,Fsought assistance from other agencies,
OL,14,Fincluding housing associations, faith
OL,15,Fgroups and organisations in the third
OL,16,Fsector.
OL,18,F"Our assessment of damage to our
OL,19,Fhousing stock across Belfast is
OL,20,Fongoing.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,442,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44113
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F441A1781187095
OL,3,C'Significant numbers' of police to be
OL,4,Con streets of NI after disorder
OL,6,F"We'll continue to work with partner
OL,7,Forganisations to provide assistance to
OL,8,Fany households requiring temporary
OL,9,Faccommodation and support.
OL,11,F"If housing support is needed, we can
OL,12,Fbe contacted on 03448 920 900 or by
OL,13,Femail at information@nihe.gov.uk."
